        <p class="govuk-body">All new digital and technology projects that handle Defence data must be Secure by Design. This includes projects built in Defence and delivered by suppliers.</p>


        <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">What has changed</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">The Central Digital and Data Office (CDDO) has mandated all government departments and arms-length bodies follow a Secure by Design approach.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">Instead of asking security experts to check if your project is secure, your team needs to design ways to continuously check security risks and mitigate them. </p>
        <p class="govuk-body">If your project has security accreditation, you need to move to Secure by Design when it expires.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body"><a href=""></a></p>      

